data.revised_prompt: A detailed depiction of a domestic cat with a multicolored, patchwork coat of vibrant oranges, smoky grays, and pure whites. The cat's ears are keen, standing upright, while its emerald green eyes gleam with curiosity. Its slender tail curls gracefully around its paws as it sits comfortably on a warm, vintage Persian rug with intricate designs in rich hues, set against a backdrop of a quaint country house. Around the cat, sun rays pierce through a window made of rustic wooden panels, casting warm, dappling beams across the scene.
